# Reggie
A Ruby on Rails web application for use in the registration of attendees to small university conferences or symposia. 

## Actions:

+ Receive information from attendees including an abstract via file upload
+ Email attendee their registration receipt
+ All registrations receipts are publicly available
+ All administrative actions (view all, edit, delete) require authorization

## Inactions:

+ Take payment


## Setup

Put setup info here.

## Hosting

Hosting is meant for Heroku and Amazon S3 for file uploads, but this could easily modified for a VPS. 
